                        I'm Israel Chidera, a passionate frontend engineer at <a
                            href="https://intercity.ng/"
                            class="underline hover:no-underline underline-offset-4 transition ease-linear"
                            >Intercity</a
                        > -[a subsidary of <a
                            href="https://myt40.com/"
                            class="text-orange-400 hover:underline transition ease-linear"
                        >
